<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<title>Zoom lens</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/swiper@8/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>


<body>
	<div class="main-wrapper">
		<div class="content-wrapper">
			<h1>Presentation of Zoom lens realization for desktop or simple slider based on images but fully build in Js</h1>

			<div class="zoom-wrapper">
				<div class="zoom-container">
					<img class="zoom-image" src="./assets/images/humboldti.webp" srcset="./assets/images/humboldti.webp"
						alt="img">
				</div>
				<div class="zoom-container">
					<img class="zoom-image" src="./assets/images/аdelie.webp" srcset="./assets/images/аdelie.webp" alt="img">
				</div>
				<div class="zoom-container">
					<img class="zoom-image" src="./assets/images/cutePenguin.webp" srcset="./assets/images/cutePenguin.webp"
						alt="img">
				</div>
			</div>

			<p>Zoom by mouse wheel, zoom square adaptive to image size. In mobile you can use only slider</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- @import "main-kit/js.kit" -->
</body>

</html>